357 S. Alvarado St.<br>
Los Angeles 90057<br>
Alex  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/lax/apa/7510386439/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
<br>
<br>
We invite you to live in this beautiful historic building in the heart of Los Angeles!<br>
<br>
We have absolutely beautiful STUDIOS apartments, available now, STARTING AT $1,525.00 per month with a one year lease.<br>
<br>
All Utilities are included except internet &amp; cable!!<br>
<br>
Walking distance from everything!! Near LACC, Southwestern University, grocery stores, night life, L.A. Live, Staples Center and much more!!<br>
<br>
Great for those who love the city life and appreciate New York style apartments. This location is a walkers paradise which means most daily errands do not require a car. The closest transit routes are the Maryland/ Alvarado 200 Metro Line and the Alvarado/ Wilshire Metro station.<br>
<br>
Most units include full bathrooms, exposed brick walls, closets &amp; hardwood floors. The apartments are unfurnished. ALL UTILITIES INCLUDED!!<br>
<br>
The building has an elevator, on site laundry and intercom access.<br>
<br>
There is no parking but there are several public garages that offer monthly services nearby.<br>
<br>
To apply, the first application is $25, any additional will be $15 each. Copies of ID’s per applicant and 2 recent paystubs per applicant are needed.<br>
<br>
To be approved, applicants must make at least 2X rent every month, have absolutely no history of evictions and must have a credit score of at least 600. Co-signers welcome.<br>
<br>
357 S. Alvarado St.<br>
Los Angeles 90057<br>
